name: NeoWs - (Near Earth Object Web Service)
description:
A web service for near earth objects. All the data is from the [NASA JPL Asteroid team](http://neo.jpl.nasa.gov/).

NeoWs is proud to power AsteroidTracker on [iOS](https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/asteroid-tracker/id689684901?mt=8) and [Android](https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.vitruviussoftware.bunifish.asteroidtracker&feature) as well as related apps.

Follow us on [Twitter](https://twitter.com/AsteroidTracker)
